div3.p:
Lancaster O. Friday 9. A.M. cloudy and damp feel about as did on
                            yesterday. nothing very particular from the y. my Wife is
                             better, 3. P.M. cold{7}

Lancaster O. Monday, 9. A.M. clear and very cold. my Wife is very Sick
                            was Sick all night was attended by Dr.  Davis. one of the
                                [-] men living {7}

Lancaster O. Thursday, 9 ½. A.M. cold and cloudy freezing hard. I feel
                            about the Same as I did yesterday. people filling their Ice houses to
                            day {5}
